            <h5 class="column-head" data-uuid="229a86e16dcc4ca3a81a3303ae9929e4">Affirmative Action and Education</h5>
            <p data-uuid="8e624002a3274cf6a55e245681a79351">Affirmative action helped African Americans and other minorities gain access to universities and certain jobs. It also created much debate.</p>
