                <h2 data-uuid="ab95eae6a800406fac92ae8b4c20991c">Cities Decline during the 1970s</h2>
                <p data-uuid="2ec039d5c1fb470daef05cc1357ab03b">During the 1970s, the suburbs grew as cities
                    declined.</p>
            </article>
